{"tid":827651,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"鏡頭下的千億作品","createTime":"2018-09-19T05:47:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-25T17:27:00.000Z","uid":35780,"like":19,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2b36f69a5af5ff2ad569a7f034fc401745713890","tid":827651,"uid":35780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T05:47:02.000Z","msg":"對我呢啲器材操作員嚟講，影相就係為左留低珍貴的時刻，而作為一個鐵道迷當然都想紀錄下呢個用咗成千憶去興建的偉大工程。<br />\n<br />\n通常靚嘅野都係脆弱嘅，又或者擺唔得耐，所以趁未正式開幕 &amp; 超強颱風未到之前就嗱嗱臨去影相留念。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/19/134101_1118e0351771bde35eb2adb245b2a636.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F19%2F134101_1118e0351771bde35eb2adb245b2a636.png&h=2de63d58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好多野到失去咗先會識得珍惜<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">（當然會有例外）</span><br />\n<br />\nBTW. 為石澳藍橋默哀"},{"pid":"b396a40ac62240bab917bd5598b9945af40ae5ba","tid":827651,"uid":8260,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T05:51:12.000Z","msg":"留名跟大師學嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78b22c9802758f31ba60ace944196f22547ae35b","tid":827651,"uid":163554,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T07:35:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c031bf29ddebffd35b2ad210c5e51905d749ecd4","tid":827651,"uid":144333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T00:10:35.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"713080a85329f1d1d89b0d15a93a0f0653e9d8a6","tid":827651,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T01:19:19.000Z","msg":"貪污賣國工程<br />\n一個唔係人人都可以上車嘅車站"},{"pid":"04071590596acde750a367e705e800322819cbf8","tid":827651,"uid":38203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T03:56:22.000Z","msg":"靚？"},{"pid":"878729548f1125e4fb5651364e2ac1a14fb3612b","tid":827651,"uid":89530,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T0